          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <div class="pros-cons-list">
            <h3 class="reviews-subheading">Pros</h3>
            <ul class="pros-cons-list-content">
              <li>Security & safety (51)</li>
              <li>Location (45)</li>
